                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)苯二氮草类常用药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)苯二氮草类常用药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>药物分类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li><strong>长效类</strong>：地西泮、氟西泮、氯硝西泮</li>    <li><strong>中效类</strong>：劳拉西泮、艾司唑仑、替马西泮</li>    <li><strong>短效类</strong>：三唑仑、奥沙西泮</li></ul><p><strong>作用特点</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>镇静催眠作用强，安全性较高</li>    <li>依赖性和成瘾性较巴比妥类低</li>    <li>有抗焦虑、抗惊厥、肌松作用</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)环吡咯酮类及其他非苯二氮草类常用药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)环吡咯酮类及其他非苯二氮草类常用药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>环吡咯酮类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>佐匹克隆、右佐匹克隆</li>    <li>作用快，半衰期短，次日残留效应少</li></ul><p><strong>咪唑并吡啶类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>唑吡坦：选择性作用于GABA受体</li>    <li>起效快，作用时间短</li></ul><p><strong>吡唑嘧啶类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>扎来普隆：超短效催眠药</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)巴比妥类常用药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)巴比妥类常用药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>药物分类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li><strong>长效类</strong>：苯巴比妥、巴比妥</li>    <li><strong>中效类</strong>：戊巴比妥、异戊巴比妥</li>    <li><strong>短效类</strong>：司可巴比妥</li>    <li><strong>超短效类</strong>：硫喷妥钠</li></ul><p><strong>临床应用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>苯巴比妥：抗癫痫、镇静</li>    <li>硫喷妥钠：静脉麻醉诱导</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(4)醛类常用药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(4)醛类常用药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>水合氯醛</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>催眠作用强，起效快</li>    <li>不缩短REM睡眠时间</li>    <li>对胃黏膜有刺激作用</li></ul><p><strong>特点</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>安全范围较窄</li>    <li>大剂量可抑制心脏</li>    <li>肝肾功能不全者慎用</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(5)褪黑素类常用药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(5)褪黑素类常用药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>药物特点</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>雷美替胺：褪黑素受体激动剂</li>    <li>调节睡眠-觉醒周期</li>    <li>无依赖性，无戒断症状</li></ul><p><strong>适应症</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>入睡困难型失眠</li>    <li>昼夜节律失调性睡眠障碍</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
