                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)抗癫痫药的禁忌证</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)抗癫痫药的禁忌证</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>苯妥英钠</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>对乙内酰脲类过敏者</li>    <li>阿斯综合征、II-III度房室传导阻滞</li>    <li>窦性心动过缓</li></ul><p><strong>卡马西平</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>有骨髓抑制病史者</li>    <li>房室传导阻滞者</li>    <li>严重肝功能不全</li></ul><p><strong>丙戊酸钠</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>严重肝功能不全</li>    <li>尿素循环障碍</li>    <li>妊娠期（致畸风险）</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)抗癫痫药的用药监护</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)抗癫痫药的用药监护</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>用药原则</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>单药治疗为主</li>    <li>从小剂量开始，逐渐加量</li>    <li>换药时需缓慢过渡</li>    <li>不可突然停药</li></ul><p><strong>血药浓度监测</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>苯妥英钠：10-20μg/ml</li>    <li>卡马西平：4-12μg/ml</li>    <li>丙戊酸钠：50-100μg/ml</li></ul><p><strong>特殊人群</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>妊娠期：避免丙戊酸钠，选用拉莫三嗪</li>    <li>儿童：注意剂量调整</li>    <li>老年人：减量使用</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)抗癫痫药的药物相互作用</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)抗癫痫药的药物相互作用</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>肝药酶诱导剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>苯妥英钠、卡马西平、苯巴比妥为肝药酶诱导剂</li>    <li>可降低其他药物血药浓度</li>    <li>如口服避孕药、华法林等</li></ul><p><strong>蛋白结合置换</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>苯妥英钠、丙戊酸钠蛋白结合率高</li>    <li>与其他高蛋白结合药物竞争结合位点</li></ul><p><strong>联合用药</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>避免相同机制药物联用</li>    <li>注意监测血药浓度</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(4)抗癫痫药的特殊不良反应</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(4)抗癫痫药的特殊不良反应</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>致畸作用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>丙戊酸钠致畸风险最高</li>    <li>神经管缺陷、先天性心脏病</li>    <li>妊娠期需补充叶酸</li></ul><p><strong>皮肤反应</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>卡马西平可引起Stevens-Johnson综合征</li>    <li>HLA-B*1502基因阳性者风险高</li>    <li>亚洲人群需筛查该基因</li></ul><p><strong>血液系统</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>卡马西平：再生障碍性贫血</li>    <li>丙戊酸钠：血小板减少</li>    <li>需定期监测血常规</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
