                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)抗癫痫药的制剂规格</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)抗癫痫药的制剂规格</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>苯妥英钠</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>片剂：50mg、100mg</li>    <li>注射剂：100mg、250mg</li></ul><p><strong>卡马西平</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>片剂：100mg、200mg</li>    <li>缓释片：200mg、400mg</li></ul><p><strong>丙戊酸钠</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>片剂：100mg、200mg</li>    <li>缓释片：500mg</li>    <li>糖浆：200mg/5ml</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)抗癫痫药的用法用量</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)抗癫痫药的用法用量</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>苯妥英钠</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>成人：开始100mg，一日2次</li>    <li>维持量：300-400mg/日</li>    <li>最大剂量：600mg/日</li></ul><p><strong>卡马西平</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>成人：开始100-200mg，一日1-2次</li>    <li>维持量：800-1200mg/日</li>    <li>最大剂量：1600mg/日</li></ul><p><strong>丙戊酸钠</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>成人：开始600mg/日，分2次</li>    <li>维持量：1000-2000mg/日</li>    <li>最大剂量：2500mg/日</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
