                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)抗抑郁药的禁忌证</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)抗抑郁药的禁忌证</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>SSRIs</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>禁止与MAOIs合用</li>    <li>需停用MAOIs 2周后才能使用</li>    <li>癫痫患者慎用</li></ul><p><strong>TCAs</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>严重心脏病</li>    <li>青光眼</li>    <li>前列腺肥大</li>    <li>癫痫</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)抗抑郁药的用药监护</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)抗抑郁药的用药监护</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>用药原则</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>从小剂量开始，逐渐加量</li>    <li>足量足疗程治疗</li>    <li>不可突然停药</li></ul><p><strong>自杀风险监测</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>治疗初期自杀风险可能增加</li>    <li>25岁以下患者需密切监护</li>    <li>前4周需频繁随访</li></ul><p><strong>停药综合征</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>突然停药可出现头晕、恶心、焦虑</li>    <li>需逐渐减量停药</li>    <li>氟西汀停药反应较少</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)抗抑郁药的药物相互作用</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)抗抑郁药的药物相互作用</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>5-HT综合征</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>SSRIs与MAOIs合用可致死</li>    <li>需间隔至少2周（氟西汀需5周）</li>    <li>症状：高热、肌强直、意识障碍</li></ul><p><strong>CYP酶相互作用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>氟西汀、帕罗西汀抑制CYP2D6</li>    <li>影响其他药物代谢</li>    <li>如TCAs、抗精神病药等</li></ul><p><strong>出血风险</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>SSRIs增加出血风险</li>    <li>与华法林、NSAIDs合用需谨慎</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(4)抗抑郁药的特殊人群用药</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(4)抗抑郁药的特殊人群用药</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>妊娠期</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>帕罗西汀可能增加心脏畸形风险</li>    <li>舍曲林相对安全</li>    <li>需权衡利弊使用</li></ul><p><strong>儿童青少年</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>自杀风险增加</li>    <li>需密切监护</li>    <li>氟西汀可用于儿童</li></ul><p><strong>老年人</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>从更低剂量开始</li>    <li>注意跌倒风险</li>    <li>避免TCAs</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
