                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)非选择性及选择性COX抑制剂药理作用与作用机制</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)非选择性及选择性COX抑制剂药理作用与作用机制</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>作用机制</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>抑制环氧酶(COX)，减少前列腺素合成</li>    <li>COX-1：生理性保护作用</li>    <li>COX-2：炎症诱导酶</li></ul><p><strong>非选择性COX抑制剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>同时抑制COX-1和COX-2</li>    <li>抗炎镇痛效果好</li>    <li>胃肠道不良反应多</li></ul><p><strong>选择性COX-2抑制剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>选择性抑制COX-2</li>    <li>胃肠道反应轻</li>    <li>可能增加心血管风险</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
