                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)解热、镇痛、抗炎药的药效、药动学特点</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)解热、镇痛、抗炎药的药效、药动学特点</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>药效学特点</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>解热：抑制下丘脑PG合成，使体温调定点恢复正常</li>    <li>镇痛：抑制外周PG合成，降低痛觉敏感性</li>    <li>抗炎：抑制炎症部位PG合成</li></ul><p><strong>药动学特点</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>口服吸收快而完全</li>    <li>血浆蛋白结合率高</li>    <li>肝代谢，肾排泄</li>    <li>阿司匹林：半衰期剂量依赖性</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)解热、镇痛、抗炎药的典型不良反应与禁忌</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)解热、镇痛、抗炎药的典型不良反应与禁忌</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>典型不良反应</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li><strong>胃肠道</strong>：恶心、呕吐、溃疡、出血</li>    <li><strong>肾脏</strong>：肾功能损害、水钠潴留</li>    <li><strong>心血管</strong>：血压升高、血栓风险</li>    <li><strong>过敏</strong>：皮疹、哮喘发作</li>    <li><strong>血液</strong>：出血时间延长</li></ul><p><strong>禁忌证</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>活动性消化道溃疡</li>    <li>严重肝肾功能不全</li>    <li>阿司匹林哮喘</li>    <li>血友病或出血倾向</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)解热、镇痛、抗炎药具有临床意义的药物相互作用</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)解热、镇痛、抗炎药具有临床意义的药物相互作用</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>与抗凝药合用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>增加出血风险</li>    <li>阿司匹林与华法林合用需监测INR</li></ul><p><strong>与降压药合用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>降低降压药效果</li>    <li>ACEI、β受体阻滞剂效果减弱</li></ul><p><strong>与糖皮质激素合用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>增加胃肠道溃疡风险</li></ul><p><strong>与利尿剂合用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>降低利尿剂效果</li>    <li>增加肾损害风险</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(4)解热、镇痛、抗炎药的临床应用</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(4)解热、镇痛、抗炎药的临床应用</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>解热</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>对乙酰氨基酚：儿童首选</li>    <li>布洛芬：退热效果好</li>    <li>阿司匹林：儿童禁用（瑞氏综合征）</li></ul><p><strong>镇痛</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>头痛、牙痛、肌肉痛</li>    <li>痛经</li>    <li>轻中度疼痛首选</li></ul><p><strong>抗炎</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>类风湿关节炎</li>    <li>骨关节炎</li>    <li>强直性脊柱炎</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
