                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">对乙酰氨基酚、布洛芬等代表药品</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">对乙酰氨基酚、布洛芬等代表药品</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>对乙酰氨基酚</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>解热镇痛，无抗炎作用</li>    <li>成人最大剂量4g/日</li>    <li>过量可致肝坏死</li></ul><p><strong>布洛芬</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>解热镇痛抗炎</li>    <li>成人200-400mg，每4-6小时</li>    <li>最大剂量1.2g/日</li></ul><p><strong>双氯芬酸</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>抗炎镇痛作用强</li>    <li>多种剂型：口服、外用、注射</li></ul><p><strong>塞来昔布</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>选择性COX-2抑制剂</li>    <li>胃肠道反应轻</li>    <li>心血管风险需关注</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
