                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)吸入装置的选择</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)吸入装置的选择</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>根据年龄选择</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>婴幼儿：雾化器</li>    <li>学龄儿童：pMDI+储雾器或DPI</li>    <li>成人：pMDI或DPI</li></ul><p><strong>根据疾病选择</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>急性发作：pMDI或雾化器</li>    <li>维持治疗：DPI</li></ul><p><strong>根据患者能力</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>吸气能力差：雾化器</li>    <li>手口协调差：储雾器或DPI</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)吸入装置的不良反应预防</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)吸入装置的不良反应预防</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>口腔不良反应</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>ICS用后漱口</li>    <li>使用储雾器减少口咽沉积</li></ul><p><strong>全身不良反应</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>选择合适的装置和剂量</li>    <li>定期评估，调整治疗</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
