                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)抑酸剂的分类及常用药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)抑酸剂的分类及常用药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>质子泵抑制剂(PPI)</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>奥美拉唑、艾司奥美拉唑</li>    <li>泮托拉唑、雷贝拉唑</li>    <li>兰索拉唑、右兰索拉唑</li></ul><p><strong>H2受体拮抗剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>西咪替丁、雷尼替丁</li>    <li>法莫替丁、尼扎替丁</li></ul><p><strong>钾离子竞争性酸阻滞剂(P-CAB)</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>伏诺拉生、替戈拉生</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)抗酸药的分类及常用药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)抗酸药的分类及常用药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>吸收性抗酸药</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>碳酸氢钠：起效快，易碱中毒</li></ul><p><strong>非吸收性抗酸药</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>氢氧化铝：收敛、止血</li>    <li>氢氧化镁：导泻</li>    <li>铝碳酸镁：中和胃酸，保护黏膜</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)胃黏膜保护剂的分类及常用药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)胃黏膜保护剂的分类及常用药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>前列腺素衍生物</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>米索前列醇：增加黏液和碳酸氢盐分泌</li></ul><p><strong>铋剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>枸橼酸铋钾：保护黏膜，杀灭幽门螺杆菌</li></ul><p><strong>其他</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>硫糖铝：形成保护膜</li>    <li>瑞巴派特：促进前列腺素合成</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
