                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)强心苷类常用药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)强心苷类常用药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>代表药物</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>地高辛：最常用</li>    <li>洋地黄毒苷：长效</li>    <li>毛花苷C（西地兰）：静脉注射</li></ul><p><strong>特点</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>正性肌力作用</li>    <li>负性频率作用</li>    <li>负性传导作用</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)非强心苷类常用药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)非强心苷类常用药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>β受体激动剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>多巴酚丁胺：短期使用</li>    <li>多巴胺：急性心衰</li></ul><p><strong>磷酸二酯酶抑制剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>米力农：急性心衰</li></ul><p><strong>钙增敏剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>左西孟旦：急性心衰</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)抗心力衰竭药分类</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)抗心力衰竭药分类</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>改善症状药物</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>利尿剂、强心苷</li></ul><p><strong>改善预后药物</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>ACEI/ARB</li>    <li>β受体阻滞剂</li>    <li>醛固酮受体拮抗剂</li>    <li>SGLT2抑制剂</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(4)常用抗心力衰竭药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(4)常用抗心力衰竭药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>ACEI/ARB</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>卡托普利、依那普利</li>    <li>缬沙坦、氯沙坦</li></ul><p><strong>β受体阻滞剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>美托洛尔、比索洛尔</li>    <li>卡维地洛</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
