                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)强心苷类的作用机制</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)强心苷类的作用机制</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>正性肌力作用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>抑制Na<sup>+</sup>-K<sup>+</sup>-ATP酶</li>    <li>增加细胞内Ca<sup>2+</sup></li>    <li>增强心肌收缩力</li></ul><p><strong>负性频率作用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>兴奋迷走神经</li>    <li>降低窦房结自律性</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)非强心苷类的作用机制</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)非强心苷类的作用机制</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>多巴酚丁胺</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>激动β1受体</li>    <li>增加心肌收缩力</li></ul><p><strong>米力农</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>抑制磷酸二酯酶III</li>    <li>增加cAMP</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)抗心力衰竭药的临床应用特点</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)抗心力衰竭药的临床应用特点</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>地高辛</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>慢性心衰伴房颤首选</li>    <li>控制心室率</li></ul><p><strong>ACEI/ARB</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>心衰一线用药</li>    <li>改善预后</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
