                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)抗心力衰竭药的药动学特点</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)抗心力衰竭药的药动学特点</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>地高辛</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>主要以原形经肾排泄</li>    <li>半衰期36小时</li>    <li>肾功能不全需减量</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)抗心力衰竭药的典型不良反应</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)抗心力衰竭药的典型不良反应</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>地高辛中毒表现</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li><strong>胃肠道</strong>：厌食、恶心、呕吐</li>    <li><strong>心脏</strong>：室性早搏、房室传导阻滞</li>    <li><strong>神经系统</strong>：头痛、视物模糊、黄视</li></ul><p><strong>ACEI</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>干咳、高钾血症</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)抗心力衰竭药的禁忌证</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)抗心力衰竭药的禁忌证</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>地高辛禁忌证</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>预激综合征伴房颤</li>    <li>II度以上房室传导阻滞</li></ul><p><strong>ACEI禁忌证</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>双侧肾动脉狭窄</li>    <li>高钾血症、妊娠期</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(4)抗心力衰竭药的特殊人群用药</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(4)抗心力衰竭药的特殊人群用药</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>老年人</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>地高辛减量使用</li>    <li>注意肾功能</li></ul><p><strong>妊娠期</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>ACEI禁用</li>    <li>可用地高辛</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
