                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)利尿剂的药理作用与作用机制</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)利尿剂的药理作用与作用机制</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>袢利尿剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>抑制髓袢升支粗段Na<sup>+</sup>-K<sup>+</sup>-2Cl<sup>-</sup>共转运</li>    <li>排钠排水，降低血容量</li>    <li>降低心脏前负荷</li></ul><p><strong>噻嗪类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>抑制远曲小管Na<sup>+</sup>-Cl<sup>-</sup>共转运</li></ul><p><strong>螺内酯</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>拮抗醛固酮受体</li>    <li>保钾排钠</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)ACEI/ARB的药理作用与作用机制</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)ACEI/ARB的药理作用与作用机制</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>ACEI</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>抑制血管紧张素转换酶</li>    <li>减少血管紧张素II生成</li>    <li>减少醛固酮分泌</li>    <li>抑制心室重构</li></ul><p><strong>ARB</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>阻断血管紧张素II受体(AT1)</li>    <li>作用与ACEI相似</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)β受体阻滞剂的药理作用与作用机制</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)β受体阻滞剂的药理作用与作用机制</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>作用机制</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>阻断β受体，降低交感神经活性</li>    <li>降低心率，降低心肌耗氧</li>    <li>上调β受体密度</li>    <li>改善心肌能量代谢</li></ul><p><strong>临床意义</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>长期使用改善心功能</li>    <li>降低死亡率和住院率</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
