                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)强心苷类的药动学特点与临床应用</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)强心苷类的药动学特点与临床应用</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>药动学特点</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>口服吸收好</li>    <li>主要以原形经肾排泄</li>    <li>半衰期36小时</li>    <li>肾功能不全需减量</li></ul><p><strong>临床应用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>慢性心衰伴房颤首选</li>    <li>控制心室率</li>    <li>改善症状</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)具有临床意义的药物相互作用</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)具有临床意义的药物相互作用</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>地高辛</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>胺碘酮、奎尼丁升高地高辛浓度</li>    <li>排钾利尿剂增加中毒风险</li>    <li>避免与维拉帕米合用</li></ul><p><strong>ACEI</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>与保钾利尿剂合用致高钾</li>    <li>与NSAIDs合用降低效果</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)典型不良反应与禁忌</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)典型不良反应与禁忌</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>地高辛中毒表现</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>胃肠道：厌食、恶心、呕吐</li>    <li>心脏：室性早搏、房室传导阻滞</li>    <li>神经系统：头痛、视物模糊、黄视</li></ul><p><strong>禁忌证</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>预激综合征伴房颤</li>    <li>II度以上房室传导阻滞</li>    <li>肥厚型梗阻性心肌病</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
