                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">硫酸亚铁、华法林、利伐沙班等代表药品</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">硫酸亚铁、华法林、利伐沙班等代表药品</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>硫酸亚铁</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>片剂：0.3g</li>    <li>成人：0.3g，一日3次</li>    <li>餐后服用</li></ul><p><strong>华法林</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>片剂：2.5mg、5mg</li>    <li>根据INR调整剂量</li>    <li>维持量：2.5-5mg/日</li></ul><p><strong>利伐沙班</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>片剂：10mg、15mg、20mg</li>    <li>房颤卒中预防：20mg，一日1次</li></ul><p><strong>低分子肝素</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>依诺肝素：皮下注射</li>    <li>预防：40mg，一日1次</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
