                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)抗血小板药分类</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)抗血小板药分类</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>环氧酶抑制剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>阿司匹林：最常用</li></ul><p><strong>ADP受体拮抗剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>氯吡格雷</li>    <li>替格瑞洛</li>    <li>普拉格雷</li></ul><p><strong>GP IIb/IIIa受体拮抗剂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>阿昔单抗</li>    <li>替罗非班</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)常用抗血小板药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)常用抗血小板药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>阿司匹林</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>心血管疾病一级和二级预防</li>    <li>小剂量：75-100mg/日</li></ul><p><strong>氯吡格雷</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>ACS、PCI术后</li>    <li>负荷量300-600mg</li>    <li>维持量75mg/日</li></ul><p><strong>替格瑞洛</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>起效快，作用可逆</li>    <li>ACS首选</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
