                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)β-内酰胺类抗生素的临床应用特点</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)β-内酰胺类抗生素的临床应用特点</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>青霉素G</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>链球菌感染首选</li>    <li>梅毒首选</li></ul><p><strong>阿莫西林</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>幽门螺杆菌根除</li>    <li>呼吸道感染</li></ul><p><strong>头孢菌素</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>代次越高，抗G<sup>-</sup>菌越强</li>    <li>第三代头孢对G<sup>-</sup>菌最强</li></ul><p><strong>碳青霉烯类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>多重耐药菌感染</li>    <li>重症感染经验治疗</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)典型不良反应与禁忌</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)典型不良反应与禁忌</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>过敏反应</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>最常见不良反应</li>    <li>皮疹、药物热</li>    <li>过敏性休克（最严重）</li></ul><p><strong>其他不良反应</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>胃肠道反应</li>    <li>二重感染</li>    <li>凝血功能障碍（头孢类）</li>    <li>双硫仑样反应（含甲硫四氮唑侧链）</li></ul><p><strong>禁忌证</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>对本品或同类药物过敏者</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)具有临床意义的药物相互作用</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)具有临床意义的药物相互作用</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>药物相互作用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>与氨基糖苷类有协同作用</li>    <li>禁止与含醇制剂合用（双硫仑样反应）</li>    <li>丙磺舒延缓排泄，提高血药浓度</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(4)特殊人群用药</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(4)特殊人群用药</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>妊娠期</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>β-内酰胺类相对安全</li>    <li>青霉素类首选</li></ul><p><strong>肾功能不全</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>多数需调整剂量</li>    <li>头孢曲松主要经肝胆排泄</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
