                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)氟喹诺酮类的作用机制与临床应用</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)氟喹诺酮类的作用机制与临床应用</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>作用机制</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>抑制DNA旋转酶（拓扑异构酶II）</li>    <li>抑制拓扑异构酶IV</li>    <li>阻碍DNA复制</li></ul><p><strong>临床应用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>尿路感染</li>    <li>呼吸道感染</li>    <li>肠道感染</li>    <li>骨关节感染</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)磺胺类的作用机制与临床应用</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)磺胺类的作用机制与临床应用</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>作用机制</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>与PABA竞争二氢叶酸合成酶</li>    <li>抑制叶酸合成</li>    <li>甲氧苄啶(TMP)抑制二氢叶酸还原酶</li></ul><p><strong>临床应用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>肺孢子菌肺炎首选</li>    <li>流行性脑脊髓膜炎</li>    <li>尿路感染</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)氟喹诺酮类的典型不良反应</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)氟喹诺酮类的典型不良反应</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>肌腱炎和肌腱断裂</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>60岁以上、使用糖皮质激素者风险高</li></ul><p><strong>中枢神经系统</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>头痛、头晕、失眠</li>    <li>癫痫发作风险</li></ul><p><strong>心脏毒性</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>QT间期延长</li></ul><p><strong>软骨损害</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>18岁以下禁用</li>    <li>妊娠期禁用</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(4)磺胺类的典型不良反应</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(4)磺胺类的典型不良反应</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>过敏反应</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>皮疹、药热</li>    <li>多形性红斑、剥脱性皮炎</li></ul><p><strong>血液系统</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>溶血性贫血（G6PD缺乏者）</li>    <li>粒细胞减少</li></ul><p><strong>泌尿系统</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>结晶尿、血尿</li>    <li>需多饮水</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
