                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)氟喹诺酮类的禁忌证</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)氟喹诺酮类的禁忌证</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>禁忌证</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>18岁以下青少年</li>    <li>妊娠期、哺乳期</li>    <li>癫痫患者</li>    <li>QT间期延长者</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)氟喹诺酮类的药物相互作用</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)氟喹诺酮类的药物相互作用</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>药物相互作用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>与抗酸药、含金属离子药物间隔2小时</li>    <li>与茶碱合用升高茶碱浓度</li>    <li>与NSAIDs合用增加中枢兴奋风险</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)磺胺类的用药监护</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)磺胺类的用药监护</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>监护要点</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>多饮水，碱化尿液</li>    <li>监测血常规</li>    <li>G6PD缺乏者禁用</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(4)甲硝唑的临床应用与不良反应</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(4)甲硝唑的临床应用与不良反应</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>临床应用</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>厌氧菌感染</li>    <li>滴虫病</li>    <li>阿米巴病</li>    <li>幽门螺杆菌根除</li></ul><p><strong>不良反应</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>胃肠道反应</li>    <li>双硫仑样反应</li>    <li>神经系统症状</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
