                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)抗真菌药分类</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)抗真菌药分类</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>多烯类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>两性霉素B：广谱，毒性大</li>    <li>制霉菌素：口服不吸收</li></ul><p><strong>唑类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>氟康唑：念珠菌、隐球菌</li>    <li>伊曲康唑：广谱</li>    <li>伏立康唑：广谱，包括曲霉</li>    <li>酮康唑：外用为主</li></ul><p><strong>丙烯胺类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>特比萘芬：皮肤癣菌首选</li></ul><p><strong>棘白菌素类</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>卡泊芬净、米卡芬净</li>    <li>静脉给药</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)常用抗真菌药物</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)常用抗真菌药物</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                    <p><strong>氟康唑</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>念珠菌感染首选</li>    <li>隐球菌脑膜炎</li>    <li>口服生物利用度高</li></ul><p><strong>伏立康唑</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>侵袭性曲霉病首选</li>    <li>广谱抗真菌</li></ul><p><strong>两性霉素B</strong>：</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">    <li>深部真菌感染</li>    <li>毒性大，需缓慢滴注</li></ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
