                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)药学信息与药学信息服务</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)药学信息与药学信息服务</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>药学信息定义</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>与药学相关的知识和消息</li>            <li>包括药品信息、药物治疗信息、药事法规信息等</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>药学信息服务</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>向医护人员、患者提供药学信息</li>            <li>解答用药咨询</li>            <li>提供药物治疗建议</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)药学信息服务常用资料</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)药学信息服务常用资料</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>一级文献</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>原始研究论文</li>            <li>临床试验报告</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>二级文献</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>文摘、索引</li>            <li>如PubMed、中国知网</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>三级文献</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>药品说明书</li>            <li>药典、临床用药指南</li>            <li>教科书、专著</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
