                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)咨询服务方法</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)咨询服务方法</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>咨询方式</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>面对面咨询</li>            <li>电话咨询</li>            <li>网络咨询</li>            <li>书面咨询</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>咨询流程</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>了解咨询者需求</li>            <li>收集相关信息</li>            <li>检索分析资料</li>            <li>提供专业建议</li>            <li>记录存档</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)需特别关注的问题</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)需特别关注的问题</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>特殊人群用药</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>妊娠期、哺乳期用药</li>            <li>儿童用药</li>            <li>老年人用药</li>            <li>肝肾功能不全患者用药</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>用药安全问题</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>药物相互作用</li>            <li>不良反应</li>            <li>用药禁忌</li>            <li>用药依从性</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
