                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)药物治疗方案的评估要点</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)药物治疗方案的评估要点</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>适应症评估</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>用药与诊断是否相符</li>            <li>是否有用药指征</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>药物选择评估</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>药物选择是否合理</li>            <li>是否考虑禁忌症</li>            <li>是否考虑相互作用</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>剂量方案评估</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>剂量是否适当</li>            <li>给药途径是否合理</li>            <li>给药频次是否正确</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)计划制定及执行</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)计划制定及执行</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>治疗目标设定</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>短期目标：症状缓解</li>            <li>长期目标：疾病控制</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>干预措施</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>药物治疗建议</li>            <li>生活方式干预</li>            <li>用药教育</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>执行计划</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>与医师沟通协调</li>            <li>患者知情同意</li>            <li>记录执行情况</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)跟踪随访</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)跟踪随访</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>随访内容</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>用药依从性评估</li>            <li>疗效评估</li>            <li>不良反应监测</li>            <li>实验室指标监测</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>随访方式</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>门诊随访</li>            <li>电话随访</li>            <li>网络随访</li>            <li>家庭访视</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>随访频率</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>根据疾病类型确定</li>            <li>初始治疗期增加随访频次</li>            <li>稳定期可适当减少</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
