                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)用药错误的分级</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)用药错误的分级</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>A级</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>客观环境可能引发错误</li>            <li>未发生错误</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>B-D级</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>错误发生但未到达患者</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>E-H级</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>错误到达患者，造成不同程度伤害</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>I级</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>导致患者死亡</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)用药错误的引发原因</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)用药错误的引发原因</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>系统因素</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>工作流程缺陷</li>            <li>信息系统不完善</li>            <li>环境因素</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>人员因素</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>知识不足</li>            <li>注意力不集中</li>            <li>疲劳</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>药品因素</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>名称相似</li>            <li>包装相似</li>            <li>标签不清</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)用药错误的环节与类型</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(3)用药错误的环节与类型</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>发生环节</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>开处方</li>            <li>处方审核</li>            <li>药品调配</li>            <li>发药</li>            <li>用药</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>错误类型</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>药品错误</li>            <li>剂量错误</li>            <li>给药途径错误</li>            <li>给药时间错误</li>            <li>患者错误</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
