                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)哺乳期用药</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)哺乳期用药</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>哺乳期用药原则</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>选择进入乳汁少的药物</li>            <li>选择安全性高的药物</li>            <li>调整用药时间</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>影响药物进入乳汁的因素</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>分子量</li>            <li>脂溶性</li>            <li>蛋白结合率</li>            <li>血浆pH和乳汁pH</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>哺乳期禁用药物</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>放射性药物</li>            <li>抗肿瘤药物</li>            <li>锂制剂</li>            <li>氯霉素</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)哺乳期用药</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)哺乳期用药</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>减少婴儿暴露的方法</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>服药后间隔哺乳</li>            <li>服药前哺乳</li>            <li>暂停哺乳</li>            <li>改用人工喂养</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>常用安全药物</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>对乙酰氨基酚：退热镇痛</li>            <li>青霉素类、头孢类：抗感染</li>            <li>胰岛素：降糖</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
