                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)新生儿用药</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(1)新生儿用药</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>新生儿药动学特点</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>肝药酶活性低，代谢慢</li>            <li>肾功能不完善，排泄慢</li>            <li>血浆蛋白结合率低</li>            <li>血脑屏障发育不全</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>用药注意事项</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>严格按体重计算剂量</li>            <li>避免使用毒性大的药物</li>            <li>禁用氯霉素(灰婴综合征)</li>            <li>禁用磺胺类(核黄疸)</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)新生儿用药</h4>        <div class=\"space-y-3\">            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">(2)新生儿用药</p>            </div>            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">                            <p><strong>常用药物剂量调整</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>按日龄调整剂量</li>            <li>按体重调整剂量</li>            <li>延长给药间隔</li>        </ul>        <p><strong>给药途径选择</strong>：</p>        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4\">            <li>静脉给药：起效快</li>            <li>口服：吸收不稳定</li>            <li>肌注：避免使用</li>        </ul>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>"
                    }
