                      "coreExplanation": "<div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">京大戟</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">苦，寒。归肺、脾、肾经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">泻水逐饮、消肿散结</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">水肿胀满、胸腹积水、痰饮积聚、气逆喘咳、二便不利、痈肿疮毒、瘰疬痰核</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，1.5-3g。入丸散服，每次1g。内服醋制用，以减低毒性。外用适量，生用</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">红大戟</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">苦，寒。归肺、脾、肾经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">泻水逐饮、消肿散结</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">水肿胀满、胸腹积水、痰饮积聚、气逆喘咳、二便不利、痈肿疮毒、瘰疬痰核</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，1.5-3g。入丸散服，每次1g。内服醋制用，以减低毒性</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">芫花</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">苦、辛，温。归肺、脾、肾经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">泻水逐饮、祛痰止咳、外用杀虫疗疮</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">水肿胀满、胸腹积水、痰饮积聚、气逆喘咳、二便不利、头疮、白秃、顽癣、冻疮</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，1.5-3g。入丸散服，每次0.6g。内服醋制用，以减低毒性。外用适量</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">千金子</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">辛，温。归肝、肾、大肠经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">泻下逐水、破血消癥、外用疗癣蚀疣</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">二便不通、水肿、痰饮、积滞胀满、血瘀经闭、癥瘕、顽癣、赘疣</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">入丸散服，去壳去油用，0.5-1g。外用适量，捣烂敷患处</p></div></div></div>"
