                      "coreExplanation": "<div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">千年健</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">苦、辛，温。归肝、肾经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">祛风湿、强筋骨</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">风寒湿痹、腰膝冷痛、下肢拘挛麻木</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，5-10g。或酒浸服</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">鹿衔草</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">甘、苦，温。归肝、肾经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">祛风湿、强筋骨、止血、止咳</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">风湿痹痛、肾虚腰痛、腰膝无力、月经过多、崩漏、咯血、外伤出血、久咳劳嗽</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，9-15g。外用适量</p></div></div></div>"
