                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "<div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">豆蔻</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">辛，温。归肺、脾、胃经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">化湿行气、温中止呕、开胃消食</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">湿浊中阻、不思饮食、湿温初起、胸闷不饥、寒湿呕逆、胸腹胀痛、食积不消</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，3-6g，后下</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">草豆蔻</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">辛，温。归脾、胃经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">燥湿行气、温中止呕</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">寒湿内阻、脘腹胀满冷痛、嗳气呕逆、不思饮食</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，3-6g</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">草果</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">辛，温。归脾、胃经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">燥湿温中、除痰截疟</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">寒湿内阻、脘腹胀痛、痞满呕吐、疟疾寒热、瘟疫发热</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，3-6g</p></div></div></div>"
                    }
