                      "coreExplanation": "<div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">附子</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">辛、甘，大热。归心、肾、脾经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">回阳救逆、补火助阳、散寒止痛</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">亡阳虚脱、肢冷脉微、心阳不足、胸痹心痛、虚寒吐泻、脘腹冷痛、肾阳虚衰、阳痿宫冷、阴寒水肿、阳虚外感、寒湿痹痛</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，3-15g，先煎，久煎</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">白附子</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">辛，温。归胃、肝经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">祛风痰、定惊搐、解毒散结、止痛</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">中风痰壅、口眼歪斜、语言謇涩、惊风癫痫、破伤风、痰厥头痛、偏正头痛、瘰疬痰核、毒蛇咬伤</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，3-6g，一般炮制后用。外用生品适量</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\"><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">白前</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">性味归经</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">辛、苦，微温。归肺经。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">功效</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">降气、消痰、止咳</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">主治病证</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">肺气壅实、咳嗽痰多、胸满喘急</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">用法用量</h5><p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">煎服，3-10g</p></div></div></div>"
